      • fromEvidence

        public static IdentityLocator fromEvidence(Evidence evidence)
        Shortcut method to construct an identity locator from just an evidence instance. The principal will be populated from the evidence, if it has one. The name will be populated from the principal if it is an instance of NamePrincipal.
        Parameters:
        evidence - the evidence (must not be null)
        Returns:
        the identity locator (not null)

      • fromPrincipal

        public static IdentityLocator fromPrincipal(Principal principal)
        Shortcut method to construct an identity locator from just a principal instance. The name will be populated from the principal if it is an instance of NamePrincipal.
        Parameters:
        principal - the principal (must not be null)
        Returns:
        the identity locator (not null)
